{
  "stem": "14387.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, what's going on here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, this is-- what, you have bacon here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Isn't this kosher?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, it's kosher style, he said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, my god.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kosher style.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I thought, my god, here have I been walking all this long way to get kosher meat and I've been eating treyf anyway, so what the heck?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll go to the supermarket and buy kosher meat, or treyf meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So from then on, no more kosher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we always observed the holidays, always have to this day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So came the time when my children had to be-- go to religious school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We thought, well, we won't send them to the Orthodox, we'll send them to the conservative.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They wouldn't go, the two boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's so much Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They don't-- we don't like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after I had this for a few weeks I thought, well, what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't force them to do something they're going to hate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we're not going to give up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But let's try the Reformed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's try it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We switched from Orthodox to Conservative, maybe we'll switch from Conservative to Reformed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sent them to the Reformed to-- well, we started with University Temple.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't seem to fit in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we sent them to Temple Isaiah, and, oh, well, they-- I mean, they-- they loved it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went right through bar mitzvah, confirmation, married by-- by-- by Rabbi Lewis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they went right through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- no-- no question about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were-- became Reformed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK, we still, still-- I still belong to Temple Isaiah, and very active.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
